headline: EQT (EQT) Valuation Check After Weather Driven Natural Gas Spike And Rising Investor Interest
summary: Why the weather shock matters for EQT (EQT) right now A sharp weather driven spike in U.S. natural gas futures has pushed gas producers into focus, and EQT (EQT) is right in the middle of that move as traders reassess supply and demand risks. See our latest analysis for EQT.
